  <span id="freeText16091395975745262981" style="display:none">When Anne and Neil leave on a one-week holiday hoping to reconcile after a two-year separation, little do they know that destiny has other plans for them. Their discovery of human bones and a bejeweled cross in the hollow of a tree open the door to the supernatural realm and the anguished life of Genevieve, a nun from medieval England.<br /><br />Can Anne save her relationship and help Genevieve her eternal rest?<br /><br />The twists and turns in this paranormal tale keep the reader guessing up to the end and weave themselves together into a quest to rekindle love.</span>
