          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/6624397.Carmen_Stefanescu"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1354955267p3/6624397.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/6624397.Carmen_Stefanescu">Carmen Stefanescu
</a></div>
<div class='goodreadsAuthorBadge'></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
79
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer1252933346575756420">Carmen was born in Romania, the native country of the infamous vampire Count Dracula.<br/> <br/>She graduated the Bucharest University, the Germanic Languages Faculty. High-school teacher of English and German in her native country and mother of two daughters, Carmen Stefanescu survived the grim years of communist oppression, by escaping in a parallel world, that of the books. </span>

</div>
</div>

